<sec>
<st>
 Applications </st>
<p>

Classification techniques have been applied to <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../001/1336001.xml">
spam filter</link>ing, a process which tries to discern <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../847/459847.xml">
E-mail spam</link> messages from legitimate emails.</p>

